views.faq_client.category2_a4:
The booking can be canceled free of charge from the App or ease.ro up to 4 hours before the start time of the booking. Cancellation of a booking less than four hours before the start time of the booking is subject to cancellation fees:

Between 2-4 hours before the scheduled time for booking, 80% of the amount paid is returned;
Between 1-2 hours before the scheduled time for booking, 50% of the amount paid is returned;
The amount paid will not be refunded if the booking is canceled less than one hour before the scheduled time for the booking.

You always have a 10-minute grace period after booking when you can cancel your reservation free of charge.

This cancellation policy is in place to compensate professionals for booking time and giving up other possible bookings.
